# zjcaod tools

## Installation
```shell
pip install src
pip uninstall src
```

## Dependency Package
```bash
pip install requests==2.26
pip install urllib3==1.26
```

## Table of Contents
- Http
  - get 执行http-get请求
  - post 执行http-post请求
  - put 执行http-put请求
  - delete 执行http-delete请求
  - patch 执行http-patch请求
